<Base
  title="Refund Policy"
  description="Alpha Factory Research Refund Policy."
>
  <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
  <p>Last updated: July 2026</p>

  <h2>Digital Products</h2>
  <p>All products sold by Alpha Factory Research are digital products. No physical goods are shipped.</p>

  <h2>No investment advice</h2>
  <p>Alpha Factory Research does not provide investment advice, trading signals, or financial consulting. Purchases are for research content only and do not constitute a financial service.</p>

  <h2>Eligible refunds</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Duplicate purchase:</strong> if you accidentally purchased the same product twice, you are eligible for a refund of the duplicate charge.</li>
    <li><strong>File delivery failure:</strong> if a purchased digital file cannot be delivered or accessed due to a technical issue on our side, you are eligible for a full refund.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Non-eligible</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Change of mind after completing a purchase.</li>
    <li>Failure to read the product description before purchase.</li>
    <li>Compatibility issues with your device or software.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Process</h2>
  <p>To request a refund, email <a href="mailto:support@yijigao.com">support@yijigao.com</a> with your order details. Refund requests are reviewed within 5 business days.</p>
</Base>
